author: The Critical Drinker
description:
In a week where we found out Daredevil Born Again's shockingly low viewing figures, Rachel Zegler has been hidden away by Disney before Snow White releases, and the Harry Potter TV show indulges in hilarious casting choices, join me, MauLer, Razorfist, Ryan Kinel and BlueCollarLoser as we talk about it all.

title: Open Bar #134 - Daredevil Ep3, Snow White Premiere, Harry Potter Casting Controversy
